---
title: Korean-Inspired Steak Tacos with Sesame-Apple Slaw and Sticky Gochujang Sauce
description: The robust and vibrant flavours of Korean cuisine are front and centre in this tasty dish. Lightly charred beef slices are topped with a crunchy apple-laced salad, as well as a zingy gochujang sauce. Your tastebuds wont believe how complementary these flavours are!
